OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776255070
OL,3,CUnique visitor attraction to close if
OL,4,Cbuyer cannot be found
OL,6,FA museum in Dumfries and Galloway
OL,7,Fdedicated to rocks and gems could
OL,8,Fclose in October if a buyer is not
OL,9,Ffound.
OL,11,FThe Gem Museum in Creetown has been
OL,12,Fopen for 45 years, but now its owners
OL,13,Fare looking for someone to take the
OL,14,Fattraction over as they prepare to
OL,15,Fretire.
OL,17,FTim Stephenson opened the museum with
OL,18,Fhis parents, and now runs it with his
OL,19,Fwife Carolyn.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776255070
OL,3,CUnique visitor attraction to close if
OL,4,Cbuyer cannot be found
OL,6,FThe pair have been looking for someone
OL,7,Fto take over the attraction since
OL,8,Fbefore the Covid-19 pandemic, but they
OL,9,Fsay this has been met with very little
OL,10,Finterest.
OL,12,FMr Stephenson said: "How do you make a
OL,13,Fdecision like that? It hasn't been
OL,14,Feasy, but we feel that it's the time
OL,15,Fto do this.
OL,17,F"We came here in 1981, I was 24 years
OL,18,Fold. I came with my parents, so we set
OL,19,Fthe place up together.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776255070
OL,3,CUnique visitor attraction to close if
OL,4,Cbuyer cannot be found
OL,6,F"That was interesting - working with
OL,7,Fmy parents. Some people couldn't do
OL,8,Fit, but it was great to have that
OL,9,Fextra time with my family.
OL,11,F"My dad had a great philosophy, that
OL,12,Fwe're not in the rock industry, we're
OL,13,Fin the entertainment industry."
OL,15,FThe Stephensons have set a deadline of
OL,16,FOctober 2026 to find a buyer.
OL,18,FIf they are unsuccessful the museum
OL,19,Fwill close, the building will be sold,
OL,20,Fand its collection of thousands of
OL,21,Fgems will be auctioned off.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776255070
OL,3,CUnique visitor attraction to close if
OL,4,Cbuyer cannot be found
OL,6,FMrs Stephenson said: "It would be
OL,7,Freally nice to keep it together, but
OL,8,Fat the same time, it is our pension.
OL,10,F"Ideally if someone would like to take
OL,11,Fit on that would be brilliant, but
OL,12,Fwe're trying to be realistic about it."
OL,14,FMany locals have been coming to visit
OL,15,Fthe museum for generations, including
OL,16,FErica Smith. She brought her daughter
OL,17,FJess to the museum, and now also takes
OL,18,Fher grandchildren there for visits.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776255070
OL,3,CUnique visitor attraction to close if
OL,4,Cbuyer cannot be found
OL,6,FDaughter Jess Harness told ITV Border:
OL,7,F"It's really sad, I can't believe that
OL,8,Fsomewhere that's been so special for
OL,9,Fus for so long is going to close down."
OL,11,FFor now the museum's future is
OL,12,Funcertain, but the deadline to find a
OL,13,Fbuyer is fast approaching.
OL,15,FMr Stephenson said: "It's been a
OL,16,Fprivilege. The main privilege is
OL,17,Fmeeting the nice people that we get
OL,18,Fhere.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
