OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776255070
OL,3,CUnique visitor attraction to close if
OL,4,Cbuyer cannot be found
OL,6,F"It's been a privilege to work with
OL,7,Fthese lovely, beautiful things, to get
OL,8,Fto know more about the exhibits.
OL,9,FThey're natural, beautiful things."
